{"tid":578623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽完毓民，我更加想打柒波叔同政府","createTime":"2018-03-02T18:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T01:59:17.000Z","uid":163529,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"da875ba59b7cbb5f8f2f2ccd9d323218cf228086","tid":578623,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:39:31.000Z","msg":"派五百幾億與民共享，<br />\n有錢人果班就退差餉，退薪俸稅利得稅！<br />\n<br />\n以張建宗為例，有九個物業，<br />\n淨係退差餉都成九皮，仲有三皮稅！<br />\n成個政府都私相授受！<br />\n<br />\n住深水埗班N無人士就咩都無，有仔女既話可能有二千！<br />\n<br />\n咁撚樣香港窮人都仲可以忍既？咁多億盈餘仲話還富於民！<br />\n<br />\n利申：我咩都分唔到都算，當我唔好彩！但真正要幫既，你又幫唔到！仲要夠膽死講與民共享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8be8b54278fdc37589ac4ad4419f48833b309b4","tid":578623,"uid":160807,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:42:17.000Z","msg":"條仆街當綜援 = 所有基層, 直頭on撚9"},{"pid":"928e734eb3c9e2c42b6efb06ff6ef69ac3b6f3c3","tid":578623,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:43:23.000Z","msg":"教主講左咩"},{"pid":"3229d21a570e65e5155029fb95e8e7df60ff0627","tid":578623,"uid":43008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T18:49:20.000Z","msg":"政府一向都係咁, 已經對香港冇希望"},{"pid":"638b2f9a35fb2079503d5a79efe56f3169a14dbd","tid":578623,"uid":81575,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T22:42:40.000Z","msg":"呢D論點洗撚聽毓民咩"},{"pid":"adbaccb8498de4bc93f304a5240c9bef64d07dd4","tid":578623,"uid":163529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"香港人真係多順民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到而家都淨係識網上屌"}]}